No. Not specifically. No. I can't remember anything, except - I remember - one Christmas, my parents must have thought we didn't know who F
ather Christmas was and I remember these presents were supposedly put at the foot of the bed and I woke up and wondered what they was and - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15603272\charrsid3755071 m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 ine was a little - box with a bottle of scent in and bar of soap something like that and it was broken and me sister's - I don't know what hers was but it was all intact and it was - something nice and - oh I }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15603272\charrsid3755071 wept}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 
 and cried but it didn't make a bit of difference, I still had to get on and be satisfied with me broken bottle and bar of soap. I remember that instance and 
they didn't - say - oh well I expect you know the situation you couldn't explain could you - a broken bottle from Father Christmas so - I remember that incident and feeling very hardly done by.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 When they had actually punished you how did you feel about it?
