Oh very resentful. Yes. I always all my life have thought I - I - not how but - all me childhood anyhow that I - that my sister was far more - by them to than I was because she needed so much care but I didn't realize it at the time that it was
 care she needed you see I thought, oh - she's getting all the care and attention and -
