\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Was there anyone in the family who sang?
