remember having to gather - raspberries and strawberries there, one school - during the school holidays I was sent there for a week. Well I had an aunt - me father - me father had a - a sister lived in Bradford. Her husband was a train driver and I used t
o go there for - school holidays, for a week sometimes, during the school holidays.
