\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 So you were only at the first one for a few months and then you came to Oakworth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Yes.
