\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Nobody took you to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Where did you have your midday meal then, with your grandma?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 I liked school. I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Oh I liked them very well. You know - we all 
got - we got on very well, I don't remember ever being punished, except once and there'd been a funeral in the church yard which is next door to the school and we all went down to have a look at the flowers and next day the schoolmaster got me out of clas
s
 and said quite casually, could I remember which of us had been down to have a look at these flowers and I racked my brains carefully thinking what could he want to know for and - I remembered these names and we all got caned. Just for going in the church
yard and having a look at the flowers, somebody must have had - complained there were children roaming around you know. Quite innocently. I remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Otherwise you felt all right about the teachers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Oh yes, yes. Those were things we were punished for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Did the teachers emphasise certain things as important in life such as manners or tidiness or punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 They didn't emphasise any of these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 What about punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Oh yes. Yes. But of course there were no - no such things as sick notes if you were off - anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 They didn't mind about your manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 No. No. We weren't there for meals you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 But manners during the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 I don't remember so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Ways of speaking, were they strict on that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 If you did something the teachers disapproved of what would happen, how would they punish the children?
