\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 It was unusual?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 
Yes, they did but only casually. Because - they headmaster recommended me for - a scholarship and sent a note to my mother and father and they wouldn't hear of it.
