n to the grammar school you know, take the eleven - take the eleven year olds scholarship and - I wasn't allowed because of course they were looking to the future and thought they couldn't afford the uniform and things like that to go to school and the fa
res. The grammar school was in Keighley you see so nothing ever came of that. But I always felt to myself to be a bright scholar except I wasn't good at grammar, punctuation and grammar. There and their and words like that.
