\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Did they frequently ask what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 No, I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Did they ever meet the teachers at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Did the other children come from similar types of home to your own or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15011252 GW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 Yes. Farmers children and - and people like us. All - same sort of - circumstances.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 You didn't have any children from wealthy homes at the school?
