No, except perhaps one - sub-normal - one or two sub-normal children who - who didn't have schools to go to, all that - they all came to the same school. Bit slower, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9522921 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 How did the children of the Irish people go on, did they come to the same school?
