\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 hey used}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15603272\charrsid3755071 , j}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10046827\charrsid3755071 ust used to say, 
oh he hasn't any shoes or he hasn't any clogs. So they were kept at home and - nowadays they can summons them. Well - as something about it can't they.
